subSubSection.paragraph:
In the literature, we could see that the number of setae and the number of articles in the antennae are reported to increase with size in the organisms (

Stevenson & Peden 
1973

; 

Geisler 
1994

; 

García-Schroeder & Araujo 
2009

). It is important to indicate the variation ranges and handle this character with caution to avoid taxonomic confusion; anyway, it is common to include the number of setae in the taxonomic keys.
